    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un fcht Rohbescha laid no-\nsteepjahs no Sewama uhs Rib-\nlu / Ainam prett Rihteem / pehz\nto laid ta Rohbescha nosteepjahs\nun tekk garr Kinneretes Juh-\nras Massu/ prett Rihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un fchi Rohbescha laid no-\nsteepjahs garr to Jardanu / un\nwinnas Gals laid irr ta Sahl8-\nJuha; Schi nu laid jums irr ta\nSemnie pehz fawahm Rohbe-\nschahn apfahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un Mohsus pawehleja\nteen Israëta Behrneem/ un faz-\nzija: Schi irr ta Semnie/ ko jums\nzaur Meslofchanu buhs par Jh-\npafchumu dabbuht / fo tas\nKUNGS pawehlejis irr tahm\ndewin Ziltim / un tat puhs Zil-\nti doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Jo ta Rubbena Behrnu\nZilts/ pehz fatwo Tehwu Nam-\nma / un Gada Behrnu Zilts /\npehz fatwo Tehwu Namina / un\nManaffus puhs Zilts / irr fawn\nJhpafchumu dabbujust.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Diwi Ziltis / un weena\npuhs Zilts irr fawn Jhpafchumu\ndabbujuchas fchai Jardanas\nPuffê / no Jerikus prett Rihte-\nteem/ prett Rihta puffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un tas KUNGS runna-\nja us Mohsu/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Schee irr to Wihru\nWahrdi / kam buhs to Semni\njun\nliht / Eeleasars tas na Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preesteris/ un Josuirs Runn-\nDehls.\n18. Un jums buhs/ no ikwee-\nnas Zilts/ weenu Wirfneek-\nremt/ par Seines Isdallischanu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un fchee irr to Wihr-\nWahrdi: No tahs Juhda Zilts-\nKahlebs / Jewuna Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un no tahs Sihmean-\nBehrnu Zilts/ Semuels Amitu-\nda Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Un no Benjamina Zilte-\nEelidus/ Kislova Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Un no Danna Behrnu\nZilts/ tas Wirfneeks Buhkus-\nJagla Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. No teem Jahsepa Beh-\nneem/ no Manaffus Zilts / ta-\nWirfneeks Anniels / Eewod-\nDehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Un no tahs Eewräim-\nBehrnu Zilts/ tas Wirfneeks Re-\nmuels/ Siwtana Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Un no tahs Sebulam-\nBehrnu Zilts / tas Wirfineek-\nFelizawans/ Parnaka Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Un no tahs Ihsaschar-\nBehrnu Zilts / tas Wirfineek-\nPaltiels/ Affana Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "27. Un no tahs Absera Beh-\nnu Zilts/ tas Wirfneeks Afunds-\nSelona Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "28. Un no tahs Nawta-\nBehrnu Zilts/tas Wirfneeks Pe-\ndaëts/ Amuda Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "29. Schee irr tee / kam ta-\nKUNGS irr pawehlejis / teen\nIsraëta Behrneem to Jhpafchu-\nnu isdalliht eeffch tahs Kanad-\n"
    }
  ],
